    compositor owns position there, so QPropertyAnimation on "pos"
    would visibly snap at animation end. Wayland path uses a plain
    show/hide toggle; XCB slide is unchanged.
  * Add Build-Depends: liblayershellqt6-dev. Older Debian releases
    packaged the headers under liblayershellqtinterface-dev; the
    CMake QUIET flag lets the build proceed either way.
